018package org.opengis.test;
019
020import org.opentest4j.AssertionFailedError;
021
022
023/**
024 * Base class for exceptions thrown when a numerical computation did not produced
025 * the expected value.
026 *
027 * @author  Martin Desruisseaux (Geomatys)
028 * @version 3.1
029 * @since   3.1
030 */
031public abstract class ComputationFailure extends AssertionFailedError {
032    /**
033     * For cross-version compatibility.
034     */
035    private static final long serialVersionUID = 7082843147964652170L;
036
037    /**
038     * Creates a new exception with the given message.
039     *
040     * @param message  the details message.
041     */
042    public ComputationFailure(final String message) {
043        super(message);
044    }
045}
